          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The gamma-ray spectra from the reactions 31P(g,pg)30S",
                " and 31P(g,ng)30P have been measured by means of a",
                " 100-cm**3 Ge(Li) detector.  The incident gamma-quanta",
                " from the bremsstrahlung beam with an end-point energy",
                " of 32 MeV were used.  The integral partial cross",
                " sections are obtained for the population of separate",
                " states of the final nuclei 30P and 30S.  The results",
                " are interpreted by making use of the state population",
                " data from one-nucleon-transfer reactions."
              ]
            }
          ],
